comments: Biyombo (CHA) is in the paint for less than three seconds when he is imminently actively guarding an opponent.
Biyombo (CHA) makes incidental foot contact with Powell (TOR) off ball.
Siakam (TOR) makes marginal contact with Graham (CHA) that does not cause him to lose control of the ball.

call_type: Turnover: Lost Ball Out of Bounds
comments: The ball is last touched by Graham (CHA) before going out of bounds.
Lowry (TOR) makes incidental contact to Bridges' (CHA) arm after the release of the jump shot attempt.
Washington (CHA) makes contact to Lowry's (TOR) arm that affects his SQBR prior to his gather.
Hollis-Jefferson (TOR) places a bent arm to the side of Biyombo (CHA), but he does not dislodge him from his rebounding position.
Lowry (TOR) makes incidental foot contact with Washington (CHA) at the end of the drive with about 9.9 seconds remaining.
Washington (CHA) and Siakam (TOR) engage during the pick and Washington releases from contact as he switches on to Lowry (TOR).

Hollis-Jefferson (TOR) steps into Rozier's (CHA) path and initiates contact that affects his FOM during the throw-in.  While Rozier's reaction is not consistent with the level of contact, the contact by Hollis-Jefferson is still illegal.
Anunoby (TOR) commits a take foul on Graham (CHA) after he has released the shot attempt and a shooting foul should be called instead of a personal foul.
Lowry (TOR) does not release the inbound pass within five seconds.
